<article class="project-badge new">
  <div onclick="location.href='<%= url_for(project) %>'">
    <a class="project-thumb" href="<%= project_path(project) %>"><%= image_tag project.image_url %><div class="focus"></div></a>

    <header>
      <h4 class="project-name">
        <div class="profile-badge">
          <div>
            <a href="index-p=developer&d=cbre.html" title="CBRE"><%= image_tag("cbre.png") %></a>
            <div class="focus"></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <a class="project-link" href="index-p=project.html"><%= project.address %><span><%= render_tag_list(project) %></span></a>
      </h4>
    </header>

    <div class="summary">
      <p>Phasellus a tellus ac augue luctus fermentum. Phasellus blandit faucibus metus in scelerisque. Nunc ac purus hendrerit lorem sollicitudin egestas et quis felis. Sed ornare, sapien at laoreet lobortis, tellus arcu hendrerit nibh, at fermentum ante ante id odio.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="financials">
      <div>
        <div>
          <div>
            <ul class='size-6'>
              <li class="type"><div><b><%= project.investment_type %></b> <label>offering</label></div></li>
            </ul>
            <ul class='size-6'>
              <li class="share"><div><b><i>$</i>1.5k</b> <label>/share</label></div></li>
            </ul>
            <ul class='size-6'>
              <li class="yield"><div><b>12<u>%</u></b> <label>yield</label></div></li>
            </ul>
            <ul class='size-6'>
              <li class="term"><div><b><%= project.holding %> <u class="short"></u><u class="long">months</u></b> <label>term</label></div></li>
            </ul>
            <div class="moneywrap size-3">
              <div>
                <ul class='money'>
                  <li class="raised" style="width:<%= number_to_percentage(project.percent, :precision => 0)%>;"><div><label>Raised</label><i>$</i>21.1m</div></li>
                  <li class="budget" style="width:<%= number_to_percentage(100 - project.percent, :precision => 0)%>;"><div><label>Budget</label><i>$</i><%= project.price %></div></li>
                </ul>
                <div class="goal">
                  <div>
                    <div class="goalmeter"><div class="progress " style="width:<%= number_to_percentage(project.percent, :precision => 0)%>"><div class="marker" style="left:<%= number_to_percentage(project.percent, :precision => 0)%>;"><label><%= number_to_percentage(project.percent, :precision => 0)%></label></div></div></div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="action">
      <button class="follow">Follow</button><button class="details" onclick="location.href='<%= url_for(project) %>'">Full Details</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</article>

